sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Human
    participant A as /approve
    participant FS as docs/
    participant Idea as ~/.claude/ideas/
    participant Led as ~/.claude/tokens/ledger.md

    H->>A: /approve

    A->>FS: Read PRD name + Done tickets from kanban.md
    A->>H: ⚠️ About to archive [feature] — type APPROVE to confirm
    H->>A: APPROVE

    note over A: PII gate
    A->>FS: Read pii-report.md
    alt No PII report found
        A->>H: ⚠️ No PII report — run /pii-check or OVERRIDE [reason]
        H->>A: OVERRIDE [reason]
    else Unresolved PII findings
        A->>H: ⚠️ Unresolved findings [list] — OVERRIDE [reason] or CANCEL
        H->>A: OVERRIDE [reason]
        A->>FS: Record override in pii-report Approve Override Log
    else All findings resolved
        A->>A: PII gate passed
    end

    note over A: Feature closure
    A->>FS: Archive PRD → docs/prd/archived/ (with archived header)
    A->>FS: Seal DEVLOG.md (APPROVED session entry)
    A->>FS: Update kanban.md (all Done + closing comment)
    A->>FS: Reset HANDOFF.md (clean state for next feature)

    note over A: Cross-references
    A->>Idea: Update idea diagram → diagram.mmd + diagram-v4-final.mmd
    A->>Idea: Update idea.md status → Delivered YYYY-MM-DD

    note over A: Token accounting
    A->>FS: Read docs/tokens/[feature].md (all phases)
    A->>Led: Roll up totals to global ledger (recalculate all sums)

    A->>H: ✓ Approved — PRD archived, session sealed, tokens logged
    A->>H: Suggest /pir [PROJ-NNN] + /update-readme
